The recommendation path produced interpretable results even with the serverless-safe pairwise mining approach. For example, the rule \emph{Organic Garlic} \(\rightarrow\) \emph{Organic Yellow Onion} achieved support 0.0073, confidence 0.2018, and lift 5.4620. The seed product \emph{Organic Raspberries} produced recommendations such as \emph{Bag of Organic Bananas} and \emph{Organic Strawberries}. The key point is not just that the rules exist, but that they are materialized into \texttt{mart\_association\_rules} and can be reused across the dashboard, notebook fallback, and written report.

